1. 转变点的热力学平衡条件：
$$
\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ - k_B T\ln p_O
=\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ - k_B T\ln p_C
$$
2. 重新整理以得到分压比：
$$
k_B T\bigl[\ln p_C-\ln p_O\bigr]
=\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ-\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\ln\frac{p_C}{p_O}
=\frac{\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ-\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ}{k_B T}
$$
$$
\frac{p_C}{p_O}
=\exp\!\Bigl(\frac{\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ-\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ}{k_B T}\Bigr)
$$
3. 通过 Hertz–Knudsen 关系式将分压与通量联系起来：
$$
\Gamma_i=\frac{p_i}{\sqrt{2\pi m_i k_B T}}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
p_i=\Gamma_i\sqrt{2\pi m_i k_B T}
$$
因此
$$
\frac{p_C}{p_O}
=\frac{\Gamma_C}{\Gamma_O}\sqrt{\frac{m_C}{m_O}}
$$
4. 令 $p_C/p_O$ 的两个表达式相等，并求解 $\Gamma_C/\Gamma_O$：
$$
\frac{\Gamma_C}{\Gamma_O}\sqrt{\frac{m_C}{m_O}}
=\exp\!\Bigl(\frac{\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ-\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ}{k_B T}\Bigr)
$$
$$
\boxed{\frac{\Gamma_C}{\Gamma_O}
=\sqrt{\frac{m_O}{m_C}}
\exp\!\Bigl(\frac{\Delta g_{f,MC}^\circ-\Delta g_{f,MO}^\circ}{k_B T}\Bigr)}
$$
